{"title":"【068】谷歌字体和ICON图标","slug":"hell0-world16","date":"2022-10-03T15:21:59.000Z","updated":"2023-06-21T11:17:28.649Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/hell0-world16.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"                font-google-icons                       谷歌字体和ICON图标    ","covers":null,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>font-google-icons</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Audioweid|Sofia|trirong&effect=fire|neon|outlie|shadow-multiple\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"./mystyle3.css\">  \n    <script src=\"https://kit.fontawesome.com/e9f22420f2.js\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"></script>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <p class=\"font-effect-fire\">\n     谷歌字体和ICON图标\n    </p>\n    <span id=\"more\"></span>\n    <p class=\"a font-effect-neon\"\"> \n        <i class=\"fas fa-cloud\"></i>\n        可以链接谷歌，得到各种字体。多个字体|隔开。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"b font-effect-outlie\"\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-heart\" style=\"color:red\"></i>\n        谷歌字体还可以随心所欲添加字体样式,在链接地址后添加一个&effect=fire,多个同|隔开。\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"c font-effect-shadow-multiple\"\">\n        <i class=\"fas fa-car\"></i>\n       图标网站font Awesome.com<br><br>\n       Icon字体图标的强大之处是，你可以将这个图标当成文本，可任意添加样式。\n    </p><br><br>\n</body>\n</html>","categories":[{"name":"CSS","slug":"CSS","count":30,"path":"api/categories/CSS.json"}],"tags":[]}